s%2Fworld-us-canada-66023691%5C%22%3EBBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20LA's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabc7.com%2Flos-angeles-vanlords-rv-renters-rvs%2F13322319%2F%5C%22%3Eabc7%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20reported%20on%20the%20rising%20number%20of%20people%20turning%20to%20the%20vans%2C%20which%20are%20typically%20parked%20illegally%20on%20the%20side%20of%20main%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiberty%20Justice%2C%20who%20first%20spoke%20to%20the%20BBC%2C%20is%20a%20social%20media%20influencer%20and%20creator%20who%20lives%20in%20an%20RV%20across%20from%20the%20Warner%20Bros.%20lot%20in%20Burbank.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20Insider%20she's%20paying%20about%20%24450%20a%20month%20for%20the%20van%20%E2%80%93%20the%20same%20amount%20she%20was%20paying%20to%20live%20with%20several%20people%20in%20a%20shared%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20van%20has%20given%20her%20some%20newfound%20independence.%20A%20table%20in%20the%20RV%20doubles%20as%20her%20home%20office%2C%20from%20which%20Justice%20posts%20TikTok%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40ImWORTHITINC%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20like%20it%20here%20better%20because%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20have%20people%20inside%20my%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20vans%20offer%20Justice%20and%20others%20in%20the%20same%20situation%20little%20more%20than%20shelter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELA's%20abc7%20reported%20in%20May%20that%20these%20vans%20don't%20have%20bathrooms%2C%20with%20many%20opting%20to%20use%20gyms%20instead.%20Justice's%20van%20also%20lacks%20an%20engine.%20That%20poses%20her%20a%20problem%20when%20she's%20deemed%20to%20have%20outstayed%20her%20welcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20traffic%20wardens%20don't%20routinely%20police%20the%20area%2C%20her%20van%20has%20got%20parking%20tickets%20%E2%80%93%20something%20Justice%20says%20she%20wasn't%20warned%20about%20at%20the%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20when%20she%20gets%20three%20tickets%20she%20has%20to%20hassle%20her%20landlord%20to%20move%20the%20van%2C%20or%20risk%20being%20towed%20away%20and%20impounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20won't%20move%20this%20thing%20unless%20he%20absolutely%20has%20to%2C%20because%20he%20has%20to%20pay%20to%20tow%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20tells%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20forced%20Justice%20to%20move%20to%20several%20locations%20across%20the%20city%2C%20including%20outside%20LAX%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20dangerous%20to%20be%20placed%20roadside%20as%20cars%20drive%20along%20with%20road%20at%20high%20speed.%20Justice%20says%20she%20was%20hit%20by%20one%20while%20out%20running%20one%20morning%20and%20ended%20up%20in%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hardest%20part%20is%20the%20unpredictability%2C%20because%20right%20now%20I%20have%20to%20leave%20it%20up%20to%20this%20so-called%20vanlord.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustice%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20looking%20for%20an%20apartment%20as%20she%20saves%20up%20money%2C%20and%20hopes%20to%20move%20on%20from%20the%20van%20in%20the%20next%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVanlords%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lahsa.org%2Fdocuments%3Fid%3D7232-2023-greater-los-angeles-homeless-count-deck%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elatest%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Los%20Angeles%20Homeless%20Services%20Authority%20(LAHSA)%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%2023%2C000%20homeless%20people%20living%20in%20sheltered%20premises%20in%20the%20city%2C%20with%20nearly%207%2C000%20living%20in%20RVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVanlords%20and%20their%20proponents%20argue%20the%20practice%20helps%20get%20people%20off%20the%20streets%20and%20into%20shelter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20vanlord%2C%20Greg%20William%2C%20told%20abc7%20in%20May%20that%20he%20makes%20between%20%242%2C000%20and%20%248%2C000%20a%20month%20renting%20out%2015%20RVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20he%20charges%20what%20a%20tenant%20can%20afford%2C%20and%20despite%20making%20a%20profit%20sees%20his%20work%20as%20providing%20a%20service%20for%20the%20homeless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20want%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20the%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELA%20Councilwoman%20Traci%20Park%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Flosangeles%2Fnews%2Fla-councilwoman-looks-to-crack-down-on-van-lords%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20KCAL%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%20she%20hoped%20to%20update%20regulations%20pertaining%20to%20RV%20rentals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOftentimes%20these%20vehicles%20are%20dilapidated%2C%20broken%20down%2C%20can't%20possibly%20pass%20basic%20environmental%20fire%2C%20safety%20or%20operability%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-pays-rent-live-van-side-road-los-angeles-homelessness-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690104691000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ba4162006a5e00194982f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-pays-rent-live-van-side-road-los-angeles-homelessness-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Liberty%20Justice%20lives%20in%20a%20dilapidated%20RV%20with%20no%20bathroom%20parked%20on%20a%20Los%20Angeles%20street%20and%20depends%20on%20her%20%26quot%3Bvanlord%26quot%3B%20not%20to%20get%20towed%20away.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rhogg%40insider.com%20(Ryan%20Hogg)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-pays-rent-live-van-side-road-los-angeles-homelessness-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Of%20Hills%2C%20Forests%2C%20Rivers%20and%20Humans%3A%20G