ews%2Funcle-pashupati-paras-rejects-chirag-paswans-claim-on-hajipur-seat-4232265%5C%22%3Esaid%20Chirag%20Paswan%20was%20technically%20not%20part%20of%20the%20NDA%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20if%20he%20attended%20the%20alliance%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20was%20in%20constant%20touch%20with%20our%20party.%20(Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Affairs)%20Nityanand%20Rai%20met%20us%20several%20times%2C%20where%20he%20respected%20our%20concerns.%20I%20then%20met%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20and%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda.%20They%20didn't%20just%20honour%20our%20concerns%2C%20but%20we%20also%20prepared%20an%20outline%20of%20our%20alliance%20for%20the%202024%20and%202025%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20today%20in%20Patna%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20his%20party%20didn't%20join%20any%20other%20alliance%20even%20when%20it%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20will%20surpass%20its%2039%20of%2040%20Bihar%20tally%20from%20the%202019%20general%20elections%20to%20win%20all%20seats%20in%202024%2C%20Mr%20Paswan%20said%2C%20claiming%20there's%20anger%20among%20the%20people%20against%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20Paswan%20has%20locked%20horns%20with%20uncle%20Pashupati%20Kumar%20Paras%20over%20contesting%20from%20the%20Hajipur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20which%20his%20father%2C%20former%20union%20minister%20and%20LJP%20founder%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%2C%20used%20to%20represent.%20Mr%20Paras%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20MP%20from%20there%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-minister-pashupati-kumar-paras-on-nephew-chirag-paswans-claim-wont-give-up-seat-4213086%5C%22%3Ehas%20repeatedly%20rubbished%20his%20nephew's%20claim%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20would%20contest%20from%20Hajipur%20this%20time%20instead%20of%20Jamui%2C%20which%20he%20currently%20represents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchirag-paswan-pashupati-kumar-paras-ram-vilas-paswan-uncle-vs-nephew-again-in-bihars-lok-janshakti-party-bjp-wants-a-merger-4213597%5C%22%3Ehas%20reportedly%20been%20desperate%20for%20the%20uncle-nephew%20duo%20to%20patch%20up%20and%20merge%20their%20parties%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20even%20though%20Mr%20Paras%20has%20five%20of%20the%20LJP's%20six%20MPs%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20recent%20tour%20of%20the%20state%20seems%20to%20have%20convinced%20the%20BJP%20of%20his%20value%20in%20consolidating%20Dalit%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20questioned%20about%20a%20possible%20merger%20after%20a%20recent%20visit%20from%20Nityanand%20Rai%2C%20a%20visibly%20agitated%20Pashupati%20Paras%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNityanand%20Rai%20%3Cem%3Eke%20kahne%20se%20kya%20hoga%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20Nityanand%20Raiji%20BJP%20%3Cem%3Eke%20authentic%20member%20nahin%20na%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%20(who%20is%20Nityanand%20Rai%20to%20ask%3F%20He%20is%20not%20an%20authentic%20member%20of%20the%20BJP)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fexclusive%2Fbreaking-views%2Fi-m-not-the-right-person-chirag-paswan-on-rivalry-with-uncle-712600%5C%22%3Ehas%20pushed%20the%20ball%20in%20his%20uncle's%20court%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhen%20asked%20about%20whether%20the%20factions%20of%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20will%20unite.%20In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20he%20spoke%20about%20reaching%20out%20to%20his%20uncle%20and%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20elders%20have%20always%20made%20decisions%20in%20our%20family.%20This%20is%20not%20just%20a%20political%20matter%2C%20but%20also%20a%20matter%20of%20the%20family.%20The%20decision%20to%20split%20after%20my%20father's%20death%20was%20my%20uncle's%2C%20and%20it%20is%20on%20him%20now%20to%20decide%20if%20the%20family%20will%20come%20together.%20I%20think%20he%20has%20already%20decided.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20Paswan%20touched%20his%20uncle's%20feet%20at%20the%20