%20who've%20created%20software%20with%20ChatGPT%20to%20get%20their%20advice%20for%20generating%20better%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Break%20down%20your%20prompts%20and%20keep%20them%20simple%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20generative%20AI%2C%20it's%20all%20about%20prompting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI-powered%20chatbots%20respond%20to%20commands%20written%20in%20plain%20English.%20Much%20like%20instructing%20a%20person%2C%20it's%20better%20to%20be%20clear%20and%20concise%20when%20explaining%20what%20you%20want%20to%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmmaar%20Reshi%2C%20a%20self-confessed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpt-4-video-games-coding-chatgpt-childrens-book-ammaar-reshi-2023-3%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bnovice%26quot%3B%20coder%3C%2Fa%3E%20who's%20used%20the%20bot%20to%20create%20apps%20and%20video%20games%2C%20said%20going%20overboard%20with%20information%20in%20prompts%20could%20skew%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20to%20think%20of%20GPT%20as%20someone%20who%20is%20half-listening%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Insider.%20If%20you%20ask%20the%20bot%20to%20do%20everything%20at%20once%2C%20for%20example%2C%20to%20create%20an%20entire%20video%20game%2C%20it's%20likely%20going%20to%20make%20quite%20a%20few%20mistakes%2C%20Reshi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20recommend%20explaining%20what%20your%20project%20is%20to%20GPT%20first.%20Approach%20it%20step%20by%20step%20and%20build%20those%20blocks%20with%20GPT%2C%20asking%20it%20how%20it%20would%20do%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20found%20it%20makes%20far%20fewer%20mistakes%20when%20you%20separated%20it%20all%20out%2C%20because%20it's%20no%20longer%20trying%20to%20keep%20everything%20in%20its%20head%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeil%20Ernst%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20computer%20science%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Victoria%2C%20said%20the%20tech%20was%20a%20great%20tool%20to%20help%20those%20who%20lack%20training%20to%20get%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErnst%2C%20whose%20students%20sometimes%20use%20GPT%20to%20help%20them%20with%20assignments%2C%20said%20adding%20technical%20detail%20to%20prompts%20or%20feeding%20the%20bot%20example%20code%20can%20help%20improve%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20recognize%20key%20terms%20and%20then%20students%20refine%20it%20by%20talking%20a%20bit%20more%20about%20what%20particular%20changes%20they%20would%20like%20it%20to%20make%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Assign%20ChatGPT%20a%20role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGiving%20ChatGPT%20a%20specific%20persona%20can%20help%20it%20understand%20what%20a%20user%20wants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiving%20the%20bot%20a%20role%2C%20such%20as%20a%20specific%20job%20title%2C%20will%20yield%20better%20results%2C%20Jason%20Gulya%2C%20an%20AI%20council%20chair%20at%20Berkeley%20College%20who%20teaches%20clients%20how%20to%20use%20ChatGPT%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-get-better-chatgpt-ai-prompt-guide%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20coding%2C%20Reshi%20suggested%20users%20start%20by%20assigning%20ChatGPT%20the%20role%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bworld-class%20programmer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20telling%20it%20to%20assume%20that%20personality%20works%20really%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20otherwise%2C%20it's%20just%20using%20generic%20programming%20knowledge.%C2%A0By%20adding%20that%20specificity%2C%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20the%20best%20results%20that%20it's%20trained%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Brush%20up%20on%20the%20basics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20specific%20users%20keep%20their%20prompts%2C%20language%20can%20still%20be%20ambiguous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20users%20still%20have%20to%20have%20some%20unders