Swiss%20Open%2C%20Asian%20Championships%20and%20Indonesia%20Open%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20pair%20had%20a%202-2%20head-to-head%20count%20against%20Asian%20Games%20silver%20medallists%20Alfian%20and%20Ardianto%20but%20they%20had%20beaten%20the%20Indonesians%20on%20last%20two%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indians%20looked%20a%20little%20subdued%20in%20the%20beginning%20as%20they%20lagged%20behind%20in%20the%20opening%20game%20but%20they%20recovered%20in%20the%20fag%20end%2C%20narrowing%20a%2010-19%20deficit%20with%20a%20six-point%20burst%20before%20falling%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20they%20found%20the%20momentum%20in%20the%20second%20game%20and%20dominated%20the%20proceedings%20thereafter%20to%20come%20up%20trumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indonesians%20played%20flat%20rallies%20at%20a%20high%20pace%20to%20open%20up%20a%204-2%20lead%20early%20on.%20The%20Indians%20were%20pegged%20back%20as%20Alfian%20and%20Ardianto%20didn't%20allow%20their%20opponents%20to%20mount%20their%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EErrors%20also%20crept%20in%20as%20Satwik%20and%20Chirag%20conceded%20a%20seven-point%20advantage%20to%20their%20rivals%20at%20the%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indians%20won%20a%20few%20quick%20points%20but%20the%20Indonesians%20managed%20to%20move%20away%20to%2016-7%20after%20Ardianto%20smashed%20one%20down%20the%20middle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20down-the-middle%20smash%20from%20Ardianto%20took%20the%20Indonesians%20to%2019-11.%20Satwik%20and%20Chirag%20won%20next%20three%20points%20before%20playing%20an%20exciting%20rally%20which%20ended%20with%20the%20Indonesians%20going%20to%20the%20net.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20booming%20jump%20smash%20from%20Satwik%20further%20cut%20down%20the%20deficit%20to%20three%20points%20but%20he%20sent%20one%20wide%20to%20hand%20four%20game%20points%20to%20the%20Indonesians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indians%20saved%20one%20with%20Chirag's%20cross%20court%20return%20before%20Satwik%20sprayed%20one%20to%20the%20net.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20game%20started%20on%20an%20even%20keel%20with%20the%20two%20pairs%20engaging%20in%20some%20delectable%20rallies.%20The%20Indians%20infused%20more%20power%20and%20pace%20into%20their%20game%20as%20they%20started%20to%20dominate%20the%20rallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indians%20opened%20up%20a%20slender%206-4%20lead%20after%20a%20Chirag%20interception%20and%20maintained%20it%20till%2010-8%2C%20with%20Satwik%20unleashing%20his%20trademark%20smash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20duo%20had%20a%20cushion%20of%20three%20points%20at%20the%20break%20when%20the%20Indonesians%20went%20wide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20cross%20court%20return%20from%20the%20front%20court%20from%20Chirag%20took%20them%20to%2017-11.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20Satwik%20and%20Chirag%20grabbed%20nine%20game%20points.%20They%20squandered%20two%20before%20Chirag%20sent%20one%20down%20the%20middle%20to%20take%20the%20match%20to%20the%20decider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatwik%20and%20Chirag%20looked%20in%20control%20in%20the%20third%20game%2C%20eking%20out%20a%209-6%20lead%20before%20going%20into%20the%20interval%20at%2011-8.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indians%20were%20more%20aggressive%20and%20managed%20to%20keep%20the%20world%20number%201%20pair%20under%20the%20pump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20resumption%2C%20a%20Chirag%20interception%20helped%20the%20Indians%20keep%20the%20three-point%20lead%20at%2013-10.%20Alfian%20and%20Ardianto%20looked%20a%20pale%20shadow%20as%20nothing%20was%20going%20their%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatwik%20and%20Chirag%20also%20dominated%20the%20flat%20exchanges%20and%20soon%20it%20was%2018-12%20for%20the%20Indians.%20Alfian%20produced%20a%20superb%20backhand%20return%20but%20sprayed%20the%20next%20one%20to%20the%20net%20to%20hand%20over%20seven%20match%20points%20to%20the%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20wasted%20one%20before%20converting%20the%20next%2C%20and%20broke%20into%20a%20gangnam%20style%20dance%20to%20celebrate%20their%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20pairing%20up%2C%20Satwik%20and%20Chirag%20have%20won%20multiple%20titles%2C%20including%20Commonwealth%20Games%20gold%2C%20Thomas%20Cup%20gold%2C%20bronze%20medal%20in%20World%20Championships%20and%20wins%20in%20Super%20300%20(Syed%20Modi%20and%20Swiss%20Open)%2C%20Super%20500%20(Thailand%20and%20India%20Open)%2C%20Super%20750%20(French%20Open)%20and%20Indonesia%20Open%20Super%201000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BWF%20World%20Tour%20is%20divided%20into%20six%20levels%2C%20namely%20World%20Tour%20Finals%2C%20four%20Super%201000%2C%20six%20Super%20750%2C%20seven%20Super%20500%2C%20and%2011%20Super%20300.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20other%20category%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20the%20BWF%20Tour%20Super%20100%20level%2C%20also%20offers%20ranking%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ci%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690100580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Fasfa332g_chirag-shetty-satwiksairaj-rankireddy-afp_625x300_19_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Fchirag-shetty-satwiksairaj-rankireddy-beat-world-no-1-indonesian-pair-in-mens-doubles-final-clinch-korea-open-title-4233603%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chirag%20Shetty%2C%20Satwiksairaj%20Rankireddy%20beat%20world%20no.%201%20Indonesian%20pair%20in%20men's%20doubles%20final%2C%20clinch%20Korea%20Open%20title%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Fchirag-shetty-satwiksairaj-rankireddy-beat-world-no-1-indonesian-pair-in-mens-doubles-final-clinch-korea-open-title-4233603%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Fchirag-shetty-satwiksairaj-rankireddy-beat-world-no-1-indonesian-pair-in-mens-doubles-final-clinch-korea-open-title-4233603%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.nd