le%20239AA%2C%20which%20is%20impermissible%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20his%20third%20reason%2C%20Raghav%20Chadha%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-see-if-parliament-can-what-supreme-court-said-on-delhi-ordinance-4228668%5C%22%3Ethe%20Ordinance%20is%20already%20under%20challenge%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bproper%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20judgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20any%20Act%20that%20may%20be%20passed%20by%20the%20Parliament%20is%20already%20before%20a%20Constitution%20Bench%20of%20the%20Hon'ble%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20it%20will%20be%20proper%20to%20await%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20decision%20before%20introducing%20the%20Bill%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThus%2C%20this%20Bill%20is%20unconstitutional%20and%20this%20House%20cannot%20consider%20it.%20I%20would%20therefore%20request%20you%20to%20not%20permit%20the%20introduction%20of%20this%20Bill%20and%20direct%20the%20Government%20to%20withdraw%20it%20and%20save%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chadha%20claimed%20the%20Ordinance%20was%20designed%20to%20strip%20the%20Government%20of%20NCT%20of%20Delhi%20down%20to%20only%20its%20elected%20arm%20-%20enjoying%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%2C%20but%20bereft%20of%20the%20governing%20apparatus%20necessary%20for%20meeting%20that%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20left%20the%20Delhi%20government%20in%20a%20crisis%20of%20administration%2C%20put%20day-to-day%20governance%20in%20jeopardy%2C%20and%20has%20led%20the%20civil%20service%20to%20stall%2C%20disobey%2C%20and%20contradict%20the%20elected%20government's%20orders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690099260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fjmvt3c_raghav-chadd