he%20festival%20to%20foreign%20tourists%20as%20well.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fphotos-ladakh-changpa-festival-tribe-lac-restrictions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Restaurant%20Employee%20Fired%20For%20%5C%22Using%20Phone%5C%22%20At%20Workplace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20a%20restaurant%2C%20has%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20fired%20from%20her%20job%20for%20%26quot%3Bphone%20usage%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F07%2F22%2Fi-was-fired-for-being-lazy-all-i-did-was-check-my-phone-at-work%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20incident%20occurred%20just%20after%20she%20had%20completed%20two%20weeks%20at%20the%20eatery%2C%20Toast%2C%20which%20is%20located%20in%20Manchester.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-year-old%20Sophie%20Alcock%20told%20Kennedy%20News%20that%20she%20secretly%20made%20a%20video%20of%20herself%20getting%20fired%20by%20her%20boss%20who%20said%20that%20she%20had%20%26quot%3Bthe%20worst%20day%20of%20work%20he'd%20ever%20seen%26quot%3B.%20She%20told%20the%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20way%20he%20fired%20me%20was%20so%20unprofessional%2C%20and%20he%20couldn't%20provide%20me%20with%20a%20just%20cause.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Alcock%20said%20that%20she%20went%20to%20the%20eatery%20on%20July%206%20and%20informed%20the%20owner%2C%20Matt%2C%20that%20she%20was%20probably%20%26quot%3Bdistracted%26quot%3B%20because%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Banxiously%26quot%3B%20waiting%20for%20her%20college%20results.%20She%20asserted%20that%20it%20was%20her%20first%20and%20only%20encounter%20with%20Mr%20Matt%20and%20that%20at%20the%20time%20he%20appeared%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bfine%26quot%3B%20with%20her%20work%20ethic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20didn't%20say%20I%20wasn't%20doing%20my%20job%20properly.%20I%20got%20out%20every%20order%20on%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20rumour%20also%20circulated%20among%20staff%20members%20that%20she%20was%20getting%20fired%20for%20her%20%26quot%3Battitude%26quot%3B.%20Ms%20Alcock%20said%20she%20found%20it%20%26quot%3Bweird%26quot%3B%20when%20another%20chef%20asked%20if%20Mr%20Matt%20had%20approached%20her.%20%26quot%3BI%20half-jokingly%20said%2C%20'No%2C%20am%20I%20getting%20fired%3F'%20and%20they%20said%2C%20'Yes%20probably%2C'%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Alcock%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20she%20emailed%20the%20owner%20to%20confirm%20the%20rumours.%20However%2C%20they%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20true%20and%20was%20confirmed%20to%20her%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20longer%20required%20...%20to%20work%20at%20Toast.%26quot%3B%20She%20told%20the%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20couldn't%20be%20bothered%20to%20do%20it%20face%20to%20face.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20approached%20her%20ex-boss%20and%20recorded%20the%20argument%2C%20in%20which%20he%20stated%20that%20she%20had%20been%20staring%20at%20her%20phone%20for%20%26quot%3Bfour%20hours%26quot%3B.%20Ms%20Alcock%20opened%20the%20screen-time%20tracker%20on%20her%20phone%20to%20refute%20his%20accusations%20and%20claimed%20that%20it%20revealed%20the%20phone%20had%20only%20been%20used%20for%20two%20hours%20and%2040%20minutes%20that%20day.%20She%20also%20mentioned%20that%20much%20of%20the%20screen%20time%20occurred%20before%20and%20after%20her%20shift%20hours.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20on%20it%20for%20about%20an%20hour%2C%2010%20to%2015%20minutes%20every%20so%20often%2C%20and%20I%20took%20two%20breaks%20to%20go%20outside.%20If%20I%20was%20on%20my%20phone%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20there%20were%20no%20orders%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Alcock%20told%20Kennedy%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20she%20claims%20that%20Mr%20Matt%20criticised%20her%20%26quot%3Bfor%20eating%26quot%3B%20during%20her%20shift%2C%20which%20included%20breakfast%20when%20she%20came%20in%20and%20lunch%20afterwards.%20Not%20only%20this%2C%20the%2020-year-old%20also%20asked%20the%20restaurant%20owner%20whether%20he%20%26quot%3Balways%20interrupts%20women%26quot%3B%20when%20they%20talk%20since%20he%20interrupted%20her%20frequently%20throughout%20their%20tense%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20really%20a%20conversation%2C%20it%20was%20me%20getting%20upset%20and%20him%20saying%20he%20didn't%20like%20where%20the%20conversation%20was%20going.%20He%20basically%20said%20I%20was%20lazy%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20worst%20day%20of%20work%20he'd%20ever%20seen%2C%20but%20everyone%20I%20know%20will%20testify%20that%20I'm%20not%20a%20lazy%20person.%20I'm%20not%20saying%20my%20shift%20was%20perfect%2C%20but%20I%20had%20extenuating%20circumstances.%20He%20could%20have%20told%20me%20how%20he%20wants%20his%20kitchen%20run%2C%20but%20he%20just%20fired%20me.%26quot%3B%20she%20argued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20outlet%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20restaurant%20confirmed%20that%20she%20does%20not%20work%20there%20anymore.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20restaurant%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOver%20our%20six%20years%20as%20an%20independent%20high%20street%20cafe%20we%20have%20striven%20for%20a%20great%20atmosphere%20for%20customers%20and%20staff%20alike%2C%20but%20accept%20that%20this%20has%20not%20been%20Sophie's%20experience.%20We%20have%20made%20contact%20to%20see%20if%20she%20would%20like%20to%20discuss%20her%20concerns%20further%20and%20we%20are%20taking%20on%20board%20her%20views%20and%20reviewing%20improvements%20we%20can%20make.%20Sophie%20is%20being%20paid%20for%20the%20hours%20she%20worked.%20We%20wish%20her%20well%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690097100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fuckeu2eg_phone_625x300_23_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%