e%20same%20medical%20centre%20after%20a%20night%20of%20hospitalisation%20following%20complaints%20of%20dizziness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20week%20ago%20I%20had%20a%20monitoring%20device%20implanted%20and%20this%20device%20beeped%20this%20evening%20and%20announced%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20get%20a%20pacemaker.%20I%20have%20to%20do%20this%20tonight%2C%20I%20feel%20great%20and%20I%20listen%20to%20my%20doctors%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20said%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20his%20Facebook%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospital%20later%20confirmed%20that%20his%20condition%20was%20good%20after%20the%20overnight%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20will%20remain%20under%20medical%20supervision%20in%20the%20cardiology%20department%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu's%20latest%20health%20scare%20comes%20with%20lawmakers%20set%20to%20debate%20the%20judicial%20overhaul%20bill%20in%20parliament%20later%20Sunday%2C%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20a%20vote%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20doctors%20tell%20me%20that%20I%20will%20be%20free%20and%20I%20will%20be%20released%20from%20the%20hospital%20tomorrow%20afternoon%20and%20will%20be%20able%20to%20go%20to%20the%20Knesset%20to%20vote%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%20prior%20to%20the%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20vote%20Monday%20will%20be%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Breasonability%26quot%3B%20clause%20through%20which%20judges%20can%20strike%20down%20government%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMass%20protests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu's%20government%2C%20which%20includes%20extreme-right%20and%20ultra-Orthodox%20Jewish%20allies%2C%20plans%20to%20curb%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20powers%20granted%20under%20this%20clause%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20changes%20are%20necessary%20to%20ensure%20a%20better%20balance%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20accuse%20Netanyahu%2C%20who%20is%20on%20trial%20on%20corruption%20charges%20he%20denies%2C%20of%20trying%20to%20use%20the%20reforms%20to%20quash%20possible%20judgements%20against%20him.%20He%20rejects%20the%20accusation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Breasonability%26quot%3B%20clause%20was%20most%20recently%20cited%20by%20Israel's%20top%20court%20to%20force%20Netanyahu%20to%20remove%20an%20ultra-Orthodox%20cabinet%20member%20over%20a%20previous%20tax%20evasion%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20approved%20in%20the%20final%20vote%20Monday%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20first%20major%20component%20of%20the%20proposed%20legal%20overhaul%20to%20become%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20proposed%20reforms%20include%20giving%20the%20government%20a%20greater%20say%20in%20the%20appointment%20of%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20have%20drawn%20support%20from%20across%20political%20and%20social%20strata%2C%20including%20both%20the%20left%20and%20the%20right%2C%20secular%20and%20religious%20groups%2C%20peace%20activists%20and%20military%20reservists%2C%20as%20well%20as%20blue-collar%20and%20%C2%A0workers%20in%20the%20tech%20sector%20crucial%20to%20the%20country's%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20tens%20of%20thousands%20rallied%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20the%20country's%20commercial%20centre%2C%20and%20near%20parliament%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20as%20well%20as%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20protesters%20rallied%20chanting%20pro-democracy%20slogans%20and%20beating%20drums%20at%20their%2029th%20consecutive%20weekly%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDemocracy%20or%20revolution!%20Respect%20existence%20or%20expect%20resistance!%26quot%3B%20chanted%20protesters%2C%20many%20wearing%20shirts%20with%20%26quot%3BDemocracy%26quot%3B%20printed%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20is%20not%20listening%20to%20us%2C%20it%20means%20it's%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20era%2C%20a%20bad%20era%2C%26quot%3B%20protester%20Idit%20Dekel%2C%2055%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%20it%20is%20catastrophic.%20It's%20the%20beginning%20of%20something%20we%20have%20never%20experienced%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Dekel%2C%20a%20tech%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Extreme%20government'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20evening%2C%20thousands%20of%20protesters%20also%20entered%20Jerusalem%20and%20rallied%20near%20parliament%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20the%20prime%20minister's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20arrived%20after%20a%20multi-day%20march%20that%20began%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20earlier%20in%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20government%20is%20an%20extreme%2C%20religious%20government%2C%20and%20hopefully%20we%20will%20take%20it%20down%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Guy%20Maidan%2C%20who%20had%20participated%20in%20the%20march%20along%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20evening%20many%20set%20up%20make-shift%20tents%20to%20camp%20near%20the%20Knesset%20as%20lawmakers%20begin%20their%20debate%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Breasonability%20clause%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtester%20Keren%20Mor%20said%20she%20was%20campaigning%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20all%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%2C%20LGBTQ%2C%20Arabs%2C%20Hasidic%2C%20all%20of%20them%20feel%20that%20their%20rights%20are%20overthrown%20by%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Mor%20told%20AFP%20at%20the%20Jerusalem%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20trying%20to%20overthrow%20the%20entire%20democracy%2C%20basic%20civil%20law%20and%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20we're%20here%20to%20stop%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtesters%20also%20got%20support%20from%20more%20than%201%2C100%20air%20force%20reservists%2C%20including%20fighter%20pilots%2C%20who%20have%20threatened%20to%20suspend%20their%20volunteer%20service%20if%20the%20reforms%20become%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20revamp%20has%20also%20dra