23%20acres%2C%20the%20ITPO%20complex%2C%20(also%20known%20as%20the%20Pragati%20Maidan%20complex)%20is%20India's%20largest%20MICE%20(Meetings%2C%20Incentives%2C%20Conferences%2C%20and%20Exhibitions)%20destination.%20In%20terms%20of%20the%20covered%20space%20available%20for%20events%2C%20the%20redeveloped%20and%20modern%20IECC%20Complex%20is%20among%20the%20Top%2010%20Exhibition%20and%20Convention%20Complexes%20in%20the%20world%2C%20rivaling%20the%20colossal%20names%20such%20as%20the%20Hannover%20Exhibition%20Centre%20in%20Germany%2C%20the%20National%20Exhibition%20and%20Convention%20Center%20(NECC)%20in%20Shanghai.%20The%20magnitude%20of%20the%20International%20Exhibition-cum-Convention%20Centre%20or%20IECC's%20stature%20and%20infrastructure%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20India's%20capability%20to%20host%20world-class%20events%20on%20a%20grand%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22tmkgsvq8%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ftmkgsvq8_itpo-complex_625x300_23_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EITPO%20complex%20(also%20known%20as%20the%20Pragati%20Maidan%20complex)%20is%20India's%20largest%20MICE%20(Meetings%2C%20Incentives%2C%20Conferences%2C%20and%20Exhibitions)%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Level%203%20of%20the%20Convention%20Centre%2C%20a%20grand%20seating%20capacity%20of%207%2C000%20individuals%20awaits%2C%20making%20it%20even%20larger%20than%20the%20seating%20capacity%20of%20approximately%205%2C500%20of%20the%20iconic%20Sydney%20Opera%20House%20in%20Australia.%20This%20impressive%20feature%20establishes%20the%20IECC%20as%20a%20venue%20fit%20for%20hosting%20mega%20conferences%2C%20international%20summits%2C%20and%20cultural%20extravaganzas%20on%20a%20global%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22ptpj6jsg%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fptpj6jsg_swanky-hall-at-itpo-complex_625x300_23_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20magnitude%20of%20the%20International%20Exhibition-cum-Convention%20Centre%20or%20IECC's%20stature%20and%20infrastructure%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20India's%20capability%20to%20host%20world-class%20events%20on%20a%20grand%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Exhibition%20Halls%20offer%20seven%20innovative%20spaces%20for%20showcasing%20products%2C%20innovations%2C%20and%20ideas.%20These%20state-of-the-art%20halls%20provide%20an%20ideal%20platform%20for%20exhibitors%20and%20companies%20to%20engage%20with%20their%20target%20audience%2C%20fostering%20business%20growth%20and%20networking%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22arn6lva8%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Farn6lva8_itpo-comples-inside-pics-_625x300_23_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20state-of-the-art%20halls%20provide%20an%20ideal%20platform%20for%20exhibitors%20and%20companies%20to%20engage%20with%20their%20target%20audience%2C%20fostering%20business%20growth%20and%20networking%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IECC%20also%20boasts%20a%20magnificent%20Amphitheater%20with%20a%20seating%20capacity%20of%203%2C000%20individuals.%20Equivalent%20to%20three%20PVR%20theatres%20combined%2C%20this%20grand%20amphitheater%20sets%20the%20stage%20for%20captivating%20performances%2C%20cultural%20shows%2C%20and%20entertainment%20events%2C%20captivating%20the%20audience%20with%20its%20mesmerizing%20ambience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IECC%20also%20has%20a%20huge%20parking%20space%20to%20accommodate%20up%20to%205%2C500%20vehicles%20of%20visitors.%20The%20ease%20of%20access%20through%20signal-free%20roads%20ensures%20that%20visitors%20can%20reach%20the%20venue%20without%20any%20hassle.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690094700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fbeukgv8o_-itpo-complex_625x300_23_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-pics-de