made%20by%20Anita%20Hill%3B%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjusticethomas%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Twitter%20fan%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20close%20to%2030%2C000%20followers.%20The%20Post%20found%20that%20the%20effort%20cost%20at%20least%20%241.8%20million%20from%20conservative%20nonprofits%20tied%20to%20Leo.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20campaign%20began%20in%20early%202016%2C%20the%20Post%20reported%2C%20when%20HBO%20was%20set%20to%20release%20%26quot%3BConfirmation%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20film%20that%20centers%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenators-at-anita-hill-testimony-weigh-in-on-kavanaugh-2018-9%3Futm_source%3Dfeedburner%26%26utm_medium%3Dreferral%5C%22%3EHill's%20explosive%20allegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20Thomas'%201991%20nomination%20hearings.%20The%20movie%20starred%20Kerry%20Washington%20as%20Hill%20and%20Wendell%20Pierce%20as%20Thomas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20person%20who%20was%20tapped%20to%20lead%20the%20elaborate%20public%20relations%20campaign%20was%20Mark%20Paoletta%20%E2%80%94%20a%20former%20Trump%20White%20House%20aide%2C%20attorney%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-paoletta-clarence-thomas-national-review-disclose-lavish-vacation-trips-2023-4%5C%22%3Eclose%20friend%20of%20Thomas%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20the%20Post%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20called%20the%20Judicial%20Education%20Project%20paid%20the%20lawyer%20about%20%24300%2C000%20in%202016%20for%20%26quot%3Bmedia%20projects.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeo%20does%20not%20have%20a%20formal%20role%20in%20the%20Judicial%20Education%20Project%20nonprofit%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Post.%20Still%2C%20he%20previously%20told%20the%20newspaper%20he%20is%20an%20advisor%20to%20the%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaoletta%20did%20not%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20of%20business%20hours%20and%20during%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaoletta%20denounced%20the%20HBO%20film%20after%20reviewing%20the%20script%20and%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20HBO's%20then-president%20on%20March%207%2C%202016%2C%20claiming%20the%20movie%20contained%20%26quot%3Bnumerous%20distortions%2C%20omissions%20and%20fabrications%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20bolster%20Hill's%20%26quot%3Bcredibility%20and%20smearing.%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELen%20Amato%2C%20HBO's%20president%20at%20the%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fstory%2F2016%2F02%2Fhbo-confirmation-219408%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisputed%20the%20assertion%20to%20Politico%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20agenda%26quot%3B%20behind%20the%20film%20and%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bquite%20evenhanded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20time%20surrounding%20the%20film's%20release%2C%20the%20attorney%20began%20submitting%20op-eds%20to%20conservative%20outlets%20such%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdailycaller.com%2F2016%2F05%2F17%2Fdont-give-hbos-error-filled-confirmation-an-emmy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDaily%20Caller%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalreview.com%2F2016%2F08%2Froger-ailes-anita-hill-politicizing-sexual-harassment-charges%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Review%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonexaminer.com%2Fanita-hill-and-the-smokeless-gun%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWashington%20Examiner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20defending%20Thomas%20and%20attacking%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaoletta%20also%20sought%20help%20from%20Javelin%2C%20a%20Virginia-based%20PR%20firm%2C%20to%20launch%20a%20website%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20160421130244%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fconfirmationbiased.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfirmationbiased.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20dispute%20or%20%26quot%3Bfact%20check%26quot%3B%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20determined%20to%20not%20let%20these%20lies%20go%20unanswered%2C%20so%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20Javelin%20to%20help%20me%20develop%20a%20media%20presence%20to%20push%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Paoletta%20told%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecords%20obtained%20and%20interviews%20conducted%20by%20the%20Post%20show%20Paoletta%20worked%20with%20another%20public%20relations%20firm%20called%20CRC%20Public%20Relations%20%E2%80%94%20now%20CRC%20Advisors%2C%20which%20Leo%20chairs%20%E2%80%94%20to%20drum%20up%20websites%20and%20a%20social%20media%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Post%2C%20CRC%20helped%20create%20a%20Twitter%20fan%20account%20around%20September%202016%20to%20post%20quotes%20from%20Thomas%20or%20video%20clips%20of%20the%20justice.%20The%20account's%20bio%20now%20shows%20that%20it's%20run%20by%20Judicial%20Crisis%20Network%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20also%20led%20by%20Leo%2C%20although%20his%20name%20does%20not%20appear%20in%20the%20group's%20tax%20filings.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F10%2F12%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fleonard-leo-courts-dark-money.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20has%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20Leo%20has%20worked%20closely%20with%20the%20group%20during%20confirmation%20hearings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20also%20helped%20create%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fanitahillcase.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanitahillcase.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20dedicated%20to%20disputing%20Hill's%20allegations%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjusticethomas.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejusticethomas.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20praises%20Th