E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20totally%20her%20(Harmanpreet's)%20problem.%20I%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Nigar%20said%20in%20the%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20player%2C%20she%20could%20have%20shown%20better%20manners.%20I%20can't%20tell%20you%20what%20happened%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20feel%20right%20to%20be%20there%20%5Bfor%20the%20photograph%5D%20with%20my%20team.%20It%20wasn't%20the%20right%20environment.%20That's%20why%20we%20went%20back.%20Cricket%20is%20a%20game%20of%20discipline%20and%20respect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20umpiring%20decisions%20in%20the%20seires%2C%20Nigar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20umpires%20wouldn't%20give%20her%20out%20if%20she%20wasn't%20out.%20We%20had%20umpires%20from%20men's%20international%20cricket%2C%20so%20they%20were%20good%20umpires.%20What%20are%20they%20%5BIndia%5D%20going%20to%20say%20about%20the%20caught%20or%20run-out%20dismissals%20%5Bof%20which%20there%20were%20six%20excluding%20the%20Harmanpreet%20and%20Meghna%20wickets%5D%3F%20We%20have%20respected%20their%20decisions.%20The%20umpire's%20decision%20is%20the%20final%20decision%2C%20whether%20I%20like%20it%20or%20not.%20Why%20didn't%20we%20behave%20in%20that%20way%20%5Blike%20the%20India%20players%5D%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-match%20ODI%20series%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20ended%20with%20the%20final%20match%20getting%20concluded%20with%20a%20tie.%20Nigar%20is%20now%20keen%20to%20carry%20the%20momentum%20forward%20in%20the%20following%20games%20for%20her%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarufa%20Akter's%20final-over%20heroics%20helped%20hosts%20Bangladesh%20tie%20the%20third%20match%20of%20the%20ongoing%20ODI%20series%20against%20India%20on%20Saturday.%20With%20both%20the%20teams%20sharing%20the%20spoils%20after%20a%20pulsating%20series%20decider%20at%20the%20Shere%20Bangla%20National%20Stadium%2C%20the%20series%20ended%20on%20level%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20it%20was%20a%20great%20match%2C%20getting%20great%20experience.%20It%20will%20help%20us%2C%20when%20we%20won%20the%20toss%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20put%20on%20230%20runs%2C%20happy%20Pinky%20got%20a%20century.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20day%2C%20we%20always%20think%20we%20are%20short%20of%205-10%20runs.%20The%20way%20the%20girls%20fought%2C%20it%20was%20unbelievable.%20After%20the%20break%2C%20we%20were%20talking%20about%20the%20two%20ways%20the%20game%20would%20go%20-%20either%20we%20will%20go%20hard%20on%20them%20or%20they%20will.%20Nahida%20bowled%20really%20well.%20To%20all%20the%20bowlers%2C%20it%20was%20an%20excellent%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20Nigar%20said%20after%20the%20match.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20looking%20forward%20to%20carrying%20this%20moment.%20As%20a%20batting%20unit%20we%20collapse%20usually%2C%20but%20from%20here%2C%20we%20can%20have%20many%20takeaways%20moving%20forward.%20Crows%20have%20been%20amazing%20throughout%20the%20tournament%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20further%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20series%20locked%20on%20one%20win%20apiece%2C%20both%20teams%20went%20into%20the%20decider%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20bagging%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20even%20after%20100%20overs%20of%20attritional%20and%20enthralling%20cricket%2C%20the%20two%20teams%20couldn't%20be%20separated.%20Still%20needing%2035%20to%20win%20the%20decider%20and%2034%20to%20tie%20off%208%20overs%2C%20India%20lost%206%20wickets%20to%20be%20all%20out%20for%20225.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690093140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fp814e578_harmanpree-kaur_625x300_23_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwe-are-looking-forward-to-carrying-this-moment-bangladeshs-captain-nigar-on-odi-series-tie-with-india-4232680%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Harmanpreet%20Kaur%20launched%20an%20open%