%20of%20Bollywood%20personalities%2C%20legends%2C%20love%20stories%20and%20government%20slogans%20have%20been%20cited%20to%20support%20their%20arguments%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fseema-haider-writes-to-president-for-indian-citizenship-invokes-celebrities-legendary-love-stories-govt-slogans-8853551%2Flite%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20outlet%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20argued%20that%20Ms%20Haider%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20reside%20at%20the%20house%20of%20her%20husband%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bmotive%20of%20the%20Indian%20culture%20is%20live%20and%20let%20live%20and%20Vasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam%20(The%20world%20is%20one%20family).%26quot%3B%20The%20petition%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20woman%20had%20converted%20to%20Hinduism%20of%20her%20own%20free%20will%20before%20getting%20married%20to%20Mr%20Meena.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPetitioner%20did%20not%20get%20visa%20to%20come%20to%20India%2C%20then%20petitioner%20took%20Nepal%20visa%20and%20came%20to%20Nepal...and%20changed%20the%20religion%20from%20Islam%20to%20Hinduism...%20on%2013.03.2023%2C%20the%20petitioner%20got%20married%20to%20Sachin%20Meena%20as%20per%20Hindu%20rites%20and%20rituals%20at%20Holy%20temple%20Bhagwan%20Pashupati%20Nath%20Mandir%2C%20Kathmandu%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20in%20the%20petition%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20referred%20to%20Pakistani%20singer%20Adnan%20Sami%2C%20who%20was%20granted%20Indian%20citizenship%20in%202016.%20%26quot%3BFamous%20singer%20Adnan%20Sami%20has%20got%20citizenship%20of%20India%20due%20to%20his%20longtime%20stay%20in%20India.%20On%20the%20same%20ground%2C%20Seema%20should%20be%20given%20Indian%20citizenship%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%20read%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fnoida%2Fif-adnan-sami-can-get-citize