that%20some%20other%20athletes%20have%20faced.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EChildress%20explains%20that%20a%20big%20mistake%20players%20make%20is%20overestimating%20how%20much%20they%20actually%20get%20paid.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJosh%20Childress%2C%20a%20former%20NBA%20player%20who%20has%20made%20more%20than%20%2460%20million%20in%20his%20career%20after%20graduating%20from%20Stanford%2C%20is%20now%20playing%20professionally%20in%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gritmedia.co%2F%5C%22%3EGrit%20Media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Childress%20was%20asked%20how%20professional%20athletes%20go%20broke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20he's%20making%20less%20money%20now%20than%20when%20he%20played%20in%20the%20NBA%2C%20Childress%20says%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20avoid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fespn-30-for-30-broke-quotes-2012-10%5C%22%3Ethe%20financial%20problems%20that%20some%20other%20athletes%20have%20faced%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChildress%2C%20who%20was%20the%20sixth%20pick%20of%20the%202004%20NBA%20Draft%20and%20signed%20a%20four-year%20rookie%20contract%20worth%20%2411.7%20million%2C%20says%20the%20first%20mistake%20athletes%20make%20is%20overestimating%20how%20much%20money%20they%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20mistake%20is%2C%20people%20say%2C%20'Okay%2C%20I've%20got%20%2411%20million%2C'%26quot%3B%20Childress%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20five%20%5Bmillion%20dollars%20after%20taxes%5D%20over%20four%20years.%20So%20that%20million-dollar%20house%20that%20you%20thought%20you%20had%20%2411%20million%2C%20that%20you%20had%20%2410%20million%20more%2C%20that%20house%20then%20becomes%20more%20expensive.%20Most%20guys%20buy%20their%20mother%20a%20house%20or%20a%20car%20or%20something.%20They%20buy%20themselves%20a%20car.%20You've%20got%20a%202-to-4%25%20agent%20fee.%20You%20got%20the%20NBA%20escrow.%20So%20that%20check%20gets%20eaten%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChildress%20says%20another%20big%20factor%20is%20the%20influence%20of%20veteran%20players%20who%20make%20a%20lot%20more%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20my%20veterans%20spent%20a%20little%20more%20than%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20Childress%20explained.%20%26quot%3BIf%20those%20are%20the%20guys%20taking%20you%20under%20their%20wing%2C%20that's%20what%20you%20get%20used%20to.%20So%20that's%20how%20you%20think%20it%20has%20to%20be%2C%20and%20that's%20how%20you%20think%20the%20life%20is%2C%20and%20you%20get%20caught%20up%20in%20that%2C%20and%20you%20end%20up%20spending%20way%20more%20than%20you%20should.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChildress%20says%20he%20did%20fall%20into%20a%20similar%20pattern%20in%20his%20career%20but%20was%20able%20to%20keep%20his%20spending%20in%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20post%20was%20originally%20published%20in%202020.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-pro-athletes-go-broke-bankruptcy%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690072937000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62e5302d4b455800188b7b82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-pro-athletes-go-broke-bankruptcy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20NBA%20player%20Josh%20Childress%20made%20more%20than%20%2460%20million%20in%20his%20career%20and%20was%20able%20to%20avoid%20the%20financial%20problems%20others%20face.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cgaines%40businessinsider.com%20(Cork%20Gaines)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-pro-athletes-go-broke-bankruptcy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Rapidly%20retreating%20Ladakh%20glacier%20may%20create%20new%20lakes'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690072398000%2C%22visual%22%3A%