ce%20Pradeep%20Kumar%20Yadav%20told%20reporters%20that%20three%20women%20had%20lost%20their%20purses%20after%20withdrawing%20money%20from%20a%20bank%20on%20Tuesday.%20Locals%20suspected%20the%20two%20women%20had%20stolen%20the%20purses%20and%20intended%20to%20punish%20them.%20Civic%20volunteers%20had%20gone%20to%20rescue%20the%20women.%20Police%20are%20yet%20to%20find%20out%20whether%20the%20attacked%20women%20had%20the%20purses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20have%20questioned%20why%20police%20did%20not%20arrive%20at%20the%20scene%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20police%20post%20was%2015%20minutes%20away%20from%20the%20site.%20Police%E2%80%99s%20considerable%20delay%20in%20acknowledging%20the%20incident%20%E2%80%93%20something%20it%20did%20only%20after%20the%20videos%20came%20to%20light%20%E2%80%93%20is%20also%20being%20criticised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Farukh%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20told%20The%20Wire%20that%20his%20efforts%20to%20stop%20people%20from%20raining%20blows%20on%20the%20women%20bore%20no%20fruit.%20%E2%80%9CHow%20could%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20stop%20such%20a%20huge%20crowd.%20Why%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20police%20come%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20the%20civic%20volunteers%20rescued%20the%20women%2C%20they%20had%20been%20severely%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20daughter%20of%20one%20of%20the%20attacked%20women%20has%20alleged%20that%20no%20proper%20medical%20attention%20was%20given%20to%20her%20mother%20and%20the%20other%20woman%20at%20the%20police%20station%20after%20their%20rescue%20from%20the%20scene.%20Instead%2C%20they%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%2C%20further%20exacerbating%20the%20distressing%20situation.%20Police%20has%20not%20confirmed%20whether%20they%20the%20two%20women%20were%20indeed%20taken%20into%20custody.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EState%20Minister%20for%20Women%20and%20Child%20Health%2C%20Shashi%20Panja%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20wom