pps-psychic-ghosted-roz-hernandez-1235677443%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fvoices%2Fnews%2Fbusy-philipps-psychic-ghosted-roz-hernandez-1235677443%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan%20Minimum%20Income%20Law%20Has%20Provided%20a%20Development%20Model%20for%20the%20Nation%3A%20Gehlot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F17105003%2FWIRE-7.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20day%20after%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20passed%20the%20Rajasthan%20Minimum%20Guaranteed%20Income%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20said%20that%20his%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20provide%20social%20security%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20Right.%20Gehlot%20said%20that%20by%20passing%20the%20minimum%20guaranteed%20income%20bill%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20has%20provided%20a%20unique%20development%20model%20to%20the%20country%20and%20hopes%20that%20similar%20laws%20will%20also%20be%20passed%20in%20other%20states%20to%20bring%20every%20citizen%20of%20the%20country%20into%20the%20social%20security%20net.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20a%20law%20and%20an%20administrative%20order.%20The%20minimum%20guaranteed%20income%20bill%20makes%20social%20security%20a%20right.%20The%20minimum%20guaranteed%20income%20law%20is%20historic%20as%20it%20is%20perhaps%20the%20first%20time%20since%20independence%20that%20social%20security%20measures%20like%20pension%20or%20minimum%20days%20of%20work%20have%20been%20brought%20under%20the%20ambit%20of%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gehlot%20said%20on%20Saturday%2C%20July%2022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20law%20guarantees%20125%20days%20of%20work%20for%20all%20families%20of%20the%20state%20and%20a%20minimum%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20as%20a%20pension%20to%20the%20elderly%2C%20women%2C%20widows%2C%20and%20disabled%20people%2C%20with%20the%20provision%20of%20a%2015%25%20increment%20every%20year.%20The%20Bill%20brings%20the%20rural%20employment%20guarantee%20scheme%2C%20the%20urban%20employment%20guarantee%20scheme%2C%20and%20the%20pension%20scheme%20under%20one%20legislation%20that%20will%20be%20implemented%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Minimum%20Income%20Guarantee%20Scheme.%20The%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20assembly%20on%20Friday%20through%20a%20voice%20vote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20the%20press%20earlier%20on%20Saturday%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20law%20is%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20similar%20social%20security%20cover%20for%20citizens%20of%20developed%20nations%20like%20the%20US%2C%20England%2C%20Germany%2C%20and%20other%20European%20countries.%20Taking%20a%20dig%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20seen%20such%20a%20law.%20Our%20Prime%20Minister%20claims%20to%20be%20Vishwaguru.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20him%20what%20he%20is%20doing%20about%20problems%20like%20hunger%2C%20malnourishment%2C%20and%20unemployment%20in%20India.%20Why%20is%20not%20making%20social%20security%20a%20right%20for%20140%20crore%20Indians%2C%20a%20figure%20he%20often%20likes%20to%20cite%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGehlot%20said%20that%20the%20law%20was%20merely%20a%20start%2C%20and%20if%20elected%20again%20his%20government%20will%20move%20forward%20in%20the%20direction%20to%20provide%20social%20security%20cover%20to%20all%20in%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20state%20governments%20provide%20very%20poor%20sums%20for%20the%20pension%20scheme.%20The%20union%20government%20gives%20Rs%20200%20as%20a%20pension%20to%20the%20elderly%20and%20Rs%20300%20if%20the%20claimant%20is%20above%2080%20years.%20Tell%20me%20does%20this%20amount%20even%20qualify%20as%20any%20financial%20support%3F%20That%20is%20why%20we%20have%20made%20Rs%201%2C000%20as%20the%20minimum%20support%20to%20the%20pensioners%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20subsequent%20governments%20in%20the%20state%20will%20have%20to%20abide%20by%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20law%20has%20come%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20next%20assembly%20polls.%20Gehlot%20hoped%20that%20the%20law%20and%20other%20such%20pro-poor%20measures%20will%20help%20it%20win%20the%20elections%20again.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20talk%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erevdi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(freebies)%20culture%20are%20distributing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erevdis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20states%20that%20they%20govern.%20The%20law%20is%20not%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erevdi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20a%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gehlot%20said%2C%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRajasthan%20is%20a%20progressive%20state.%20Rajasthan%20was%20also%20the%20first%20state%20to%20implement%20Right%20to%20Information%2C%20Right%20to%20Health%2C%20and%20the%20Minimum%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20before%20it%20became%20national%20laws%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%20chief%20minister%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20new%20law%20will%20be%20financed%20from%20the%20improved%20financial%20health%20of%20the%20state%20under%20his%20leadership.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20introduced%20any%20new%20tax.%20Instead%2C%20our%20revenues%20have%20increased%20by%2017%25.%20Our%20fiscal%20deficit%20has%20also%20come%20down%20from%209.25%25%20from%20the%20time%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20to%20around%203%25%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGehlot%20said%20he%20was%20waiting%20for%20the%20governor%20to%20approve%20the%20law%2C%20and%20hopes%20to%20frame%20the%20rules%20and%20have%20the%20law%20implemented%20by%20August%2015%2C%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20of%20such%20a%20law%20becoming%20a%20burden%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20exchequer%20is%20untrue%2C%20as%20is%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20about%20the%20deteriorating%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20NCRB%20figures%2C%20the%20BJP-ruled%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20at%20the%20top%20in%20the%20list%20of%20crimes%20against%20women.%20Gujarat%20is%20ranked%20the%20No.1%20in%20cases%20of%20custodial%20deaths.%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20is%20No.1%20in%20cases%20of%20murders%20and%20kidnapping.%20Rajasthan%20is%20way%20below%20in%20the%20list%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gehlot%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20hike%20in%20some%20of%20the%20crimes%20in%20Rajasthan%20is%20because%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20his%20government%20made%20registering%20FIRs%20compulsory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20increase%20in%20figures%20of%20different%20crimes%20has%20happened%20because%20now%20common%20people%20can%20get%20cases%20registered%20easily%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGehlot%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20should%20answer%20why%20Modi%20could%20not%20deliver%20on%20his%20promise%20of%20generating%202%20crore%20jobs%20every%20year.%20%E2%80%9CToday%20he%20is%20himself%20giving%20appointment%20letters%20to%2080%2C000%20people%20to%20generate%20publicity.%20No%20one%20can%20compete%20with%20Modi%20ji%20in%20marketing.%20He%20came%20to%20Sikar%20and%20said%20that%20he%20is%20spending%20Rs%2020000%20crore%20in%20direct%20benefit%20transfer%20to%209%20crore%20people.%20All%20of%20it%20is%20marketing.%20The%20Rajasthan%20government%20spends%20Rs%2012000%20crore%20in%20subsidising%20electricity%20alone.%20Our%20pension%20scheme%20is%20worth%20around%20Rs%2012-13000%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690034845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F17105003%2FWIRE-7.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-minimum-income-law-has-provided-a-development-model-for-the-nation-gehlot%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Those%20who%20talk%20about%20revdi%20(freebies)%20culture%20are%20distributing%20revdis%20in%20the%20states%20that%20they%20govern.%20The%20Rajasthan%20law%20is%20not%20a%20revdi%2C%20but%20a%20right%2C'%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-minimum-income-law-has-provided-a-development-model-for-the-nation-gehlot%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20NSUI%20Stages%20Protest%20at%20DU%20Over%20Rape%20Cases%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Jodhpur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F22191209%2Fimage_50756097-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20July%2020%2C%20National%20Students%20of%20India%20(NSUI)%2C%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20held%20a%20march%20from%20Vishwavidyalaya%20Metro%20Station%20to%20Delhi%20University%E2%80%99s%20Arts%20Faculty%20over%20the%20Jodhpur%20minor%20girl%20rape%20case%20and%20the%20video%20of%20Manipur%20girls%20being%20paraded%20nakedly%20on%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20march%20by%20NSUI%20was%20in%20response%20to%20the%20right-wing%20student%20organisation%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%20which%20held%20a%20protest%20a%20few%20days%20back%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Bikaner%20House%20against%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20questioned%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20over%20alleged%20law%20and%20order%20collapse%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20NSUI%20attacked%20ABVP%20for%20their%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cdual%20standard%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20accused%20caught%20in%20Jodhpur%20minor%20girl%20rape%20case%20were%20associated%20with%20ABVP%2C%20as%20mentioned%20by%20Rajasthan%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20several%20protesting%20NSUI%20activists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Manipur%20incident%20is%20a%20shame%20for%20our%20entire%20country.%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20said%20anything%20about%20it.%20He%E2%80%99s%20enjoying%20his%20foreign%20trips.%20Looks%20like%20he%20is%20our%20%E2%80%98Aish%20Mantri%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20protesting%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20minor%20girl%20in%20Jodhpur%20was%20raped%20by%20ABVP%20people%20due%20to%20ticket%20distribution%20in%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20union%20election.%20As%20elections%20are%20also%20approaching%20in%20Delhi%20University%2C%20we%20are%20making%20girls%20here%20aware%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20ABVP%20and%20their%20activists%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20female%20protestor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FaBRHEmT_bjE%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690033642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F22191209%2Fimage_50756097-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-nsui-stages-protest-at-du-over-rape-cases-in-manipur-jodhpur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress-backed%20student%20outfit%20attacked%20ABVP%20for%20its%20'dual%20standards'%20as%20the%20accused%20caught%20in%20Jodhpur%20minor%20girl%20rape%20case%20were%20associated%20with%20ABVP%2C%20which%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-nsui-stages-protest-at-du-over-rape-cases-in-manipur-jodhpur%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20After%20Strip-Parade%20Horror%2C%20More%20Cases%20of%20Sexual%20Assault%20Surface%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20the%20video%20of%20two%20Manipuri%20women%20who%20were%20paraded%20naked%20went%20viral%2C%20more%20cases%20of%20sexual%20assault%20against%20women%20in%20the%20violence-hit%20state%20are%20coming%20to%20light%20despite%20an%20internet%20ban%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%204%2C%20two%20women%20from%20Kangpokpi%20who%20worked%20at%20a%20carwash%20were%20gang-raped%20at%20their%20workplace%2C%20dragged%20out%2C%20and%20left%20to%20die%20by%20a%20mob%20in%20Imphal%2C%20the%20state%20capital.%20The%20brutal%20incident%20happened%20on%20the%20very%20same%20day%20when%20the%20strip-parade%20horror%20unfolded%2040%20kms%20away%20in%20Thoubal%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fimphal%2Fon-day-of-manipur-mob-horror-2-gang-raped-killed-40km-away%2Farticleshow%2F102024469.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20male%20friend%20of%20the%20women%2C%20who%20saw%20an%20ambulance%20pick%20them%20up%2C%20reached%20the%20hospital%20the%20next%20day%20and%20was%20told%20they%20had%20succumbed%20to%20the%20injuries.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20dragged%20one%20of%20them%20inside%2C%20switched%20off%20the%20lights%2C%20and%20took%20turns%20raping%20her.%20Then%20they%20did%20the%20same%20to%20my%20other%20co-worker.%20They%20gagged%20both%20with%20clothes%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20screaming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20women%20in%20that%20particular%20mob%20encouraged%20men%20to%20take%20the%20women%20into%20a%20room%20and%20assault%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%2C%20the%20women%20were%20dragged%20out%20of%20the%20room%20and%20were%20dumped%20near%20a%20sawmill%20in%20the%20vicinity.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20clothes%20were%20torn%2C%20their%20hair%20chopped%20off%2C%20and%20their%20bodies%20covered%20in%20blood%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20man%2C%20also%20a%20tribal%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20conveyed%20the%20information%20to%20a%20cousin%20of%20one%20of%20the%20women%20who%20was%20hiding%20in%20a%20church%20to%20escape%20the%20clashes%20outside.%20It%20was%20only%20when%20the%20cousin%20in%20question%20was%20evacuated%20to%20Kangpokpi%20by%20Assam%20Rifles%20the%20families%20of%20the%20women%20got%20to%20know%20of%20what%20had%20happened%20to%20their%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-imphal-violence-daughters-killed%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20a%20detailed%20account%20by%20the%20fathers%20of%20the%20women%20%E2%80%93%20the%20women%20were%20aged%2021%20and%2024.%20The%20report%20was%20published%20on%20May%2029%2C%20giving%20a%20blow-by-blow%20account%20of%20how%20the%20crime%20unfolded%20and%20what%20happened%20next.%20One%20of%20the%20fathers%20had%20then%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20might%20have%20been%20sexually%20abused%20too%2C%20though%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20it%20for%20sure%20yet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20suo%20muto%20FIR%20was%20registered%20at%20Porompat%20police%20station%20in%20Imphal%20East%20district.%20Later%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20one%20of%20the%20two%20women%2C%20after%20much%20hesitation%2C%20filed%20a%20zero%20FIR%20at%20Saikul%20police%20station%20on%20May%2016.%20Zero%20FIRs%20are%20filed%20at%20any%20police%20station%20irrespective%20of%20jurisdiction.%20The%20FIR%20was%20then%20transferred%20to%20the%20Porompat%20police%20station%20on%20June%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20family%20member%20of%20one%20of%20the%20women%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fin-manipur-another-fir-on-rape-murder-of-2-young-women-family-in-dark-about-probe-8853540%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20still%20haven%E2%80%99t%20received%20any%20post-mortem%20report%20from%20the%20police%20although%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20more%20than%20a%20month%20since%20the%20FIR%20was%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWoman%20set%20ablaze%20by%20a%20mob%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20photo%20of%20a%20charred%20body%20of%20a%2045-year-old%20woman%20has%20recently%20surfaced%20online%2C%20following%20the%20video%20of%20strip-parade%20horror%20came%20to%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fwomen-were-stripped-raped-set-ablaze-in-manipur-more-cases-surface%2Farticle67106726.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Pastor%20Thianna%20Vaiphei%20Sauntak%20from%20Pheitaiching%20village%20said%20he%20had%20found%20the%20semi-charred%20body%20of%20the%2045-year-old%20mother%20of%20two%20on%20May%207%2C%20a%20day%20after%20a%20large%20mob%20had%20attacked%20the%20village.%20He%20said%20he%20went%20there%20under%20army%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20body%20was%20half%20burnt%2C%20she%20was%20naked.%20The%20body%20was%20taken%20away%20to%20a%20government%20hospital%20in%20Imphal%2C%20we%20do%20not%20know%20where%20it%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sauntak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20that%20armed%20men%2C%20wearing%20black%20shirts%2C%20had%20descended%20on%20the%20village%20on%20May%206.%20He%20claimed%20that%20Manipur%20Police%20commandos%20had%20accompanied%20the%20mob.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20our%20houses%20were%20torched%2C%20most%20villagers%20were%20able%20to%20flee%20the%20scene.