nal%20level%20in%20Spain.%20But%20after%20centre-left%20Prime%20Minister%20Pedro%20Sanchez%20called%20snap%20parliamentary%20elections%20for%20July%2023%20%E2%80%93%20elections%20were%20originally%20slated%20for%20later%20this%20year%20%E2%80%93%20the%20eastern%20coastal%20city%20represents%20a%20glimpse%20of%20what%20might%20happen%20on%20the%20national%20level%20if%20Sanchez%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20gamble%20goes%20awry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20four%20years%20in%20government%2C%20the%20coalition%20between%20the%20Socialists%C2%A0and%20its%20far-left%20junior%20partner%20Unidas%20Podemos%20(%E2%80%9CUnited%20We%20Can%E2%80%9D)%20could%20easily%20lose%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20pre-Election%20Day%20opinion%20polls%20showed%20PP%20with%20a%20comfortable%20lead%20over%20the%20Socialists%20but%20short%20of%20an%20outright%20majority%20without%20Vox%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20according%20to%20the%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%20Even%20then%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20could%20still%20fall%20short%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20seats%20needed%20to%20form%20a%20right-wing%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20especially%20true%20because%20the%20gap%20between%20the%20two%20major%20parties%20has%20closed%20in%20recent%20weeks.%20Sumar%2C%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fspains-left-proposes-20000-payments-for-young-adults%2Fa-66165333%5C%22%3Eleft-wing%20alliance%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20includes%20Unidas%20Podemos%2C%20is%20running%20neck-and-neck%20with%20Vox%C2%A0and%20could%20potentially%C2%A0team%20up%20with%20the%20Socialists%20to%20give%20Sanchez%20a%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVox%20poised%20to%20play%20kingmaker%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20just%20a%20day%20to%20go%20until%20Election%20Day%2C%20the%20outcome%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20But%20if%20Spain%20indeed%20swings%20to%20the%20right%2C%20it%20may%20well%20follow%20recent%20electoral%20trends%20in%20other%20European%20countries