0million%20had%20by%20far%20the%20highest%20unemployment%20rate%20in%20the%20EU%20in%20May%2C%20at%2012.7%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20approaches%20Election%20Day%2C%20Sanchez%20has%20tried%20to%20energize%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20base%20by%C2%A0invoking%C2%A0centrist%20voters%E2%80%99%20fears%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20a%20right-wing%20coalition.%20Part%20of%20the%20logic%20in%20calling%20snap%20elections%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20the%20general%20poll%20was%20originally%20set%20for%20much%20later%20this%20year%C2%A0%E2%80%94%C2%A0was%20to%20quickly%20unify%20the%20left%2C%20Encarnacion%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFeijoo%20has%20slammed%20the%20photogenic%2C%20internationally%20popular%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20style%20of%20government%2C%20which%20the%20PP%20dubs%20%E2%80%9CSanchismo.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0The%20conservative%20leader%20has%20accused%20Sanchez%20of%20centering%20the%20campaign%20on%20his%20personality%C2%A0and%20of%20flip-flopping%20on%20important%20issues.%20Sanchez%2C%20Feijoo%20said%20in%20a%20speech%20last%20Friday%2C%20has%20made%20his%20career%20on%20%E2%80%9Cagreeing%20to%20anything%20with%20anyone%20in%20order%20to%20get%20into%20power%20and%20stay%20there%2C%20lying%20about%20important%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight-wing%20leaders%20have%20also%20criticised%20Sanchez%20for%20working%20with%20Catalan%20and%20Basque%20independence%20forces%20to%20get%20certain%20policies%20over%20the%20line.%20He%20also%20pardoned%20nine%20jailed%20Catalonian%20independence%20leaders%20in%202021%2C%20a%20move%20that%20earned%20him%20strong%20rebukes%20from%20PP%20and%20Vox.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanchez%E2%80%99s%20big%20bet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchez%20has%20staked%20his%20political%20career%20on%20a%20risky%20calculation%3A%20That%20holding%20early%20elections%20will%20help%20crystallise%20support%20behind%20his%20party.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20his%20personal%20performance%20that%20seals%