ligious%20assembly.%20The%20complainant%2C%20Sawan%20Lot%2C%20stated%20in%20the%20FIR%20that%20the%20entire%20incident%20was%20recorded%20by%20Indore%20resident%20Masoom%20Jaiswal%20on%20his%20phone.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20incident%20has%20deeply%20hurt%20my%20religious%20sentiments%20and%20the%20entire%20society.%20We%20demand%20appropriate%20action%20in%20the%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ujjain%20police%20arrested%20three%20individuals%2C%20including%20two%20minors%20and%20an%2018-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20with%20Akbar%20Hussain%2C%20the%20uncle%20of%20two%20of%20the%20accused%20individuals.%20Hussain%20and%20two%20of%20his%20brothers%20ran%20a%20shop%20and%20resided%20with%20their%20families%20in%20the%20same%20house%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20demolished%20by%20the%20authorities.%20When%20this%20reporter%20reached%20him%2C%20Hussain%20was%20busy%20clearing%20the%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETracing%20the%20events%20of%20July%2017%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHussain%20recalled%20the%20evening%20of%20July%2017.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20administration%20ordered%20all%20shops%20to%20be%20shut%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9CMahakal%20Ki%20Sawari%E2%80%9D%20procession.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20inside%20our%20home%20to%20rest%20and%20the%20kids%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20terrace.%20A%20few%20men%20from%20the%20procession%20shot%20their%20purported%20videos%20and%20began%20protesting%20outside%20the%20Kharakua%20police%20station.%20Ignorant%20of%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20we%20reopened%20the%20shop%20when%20the%20Yatra%20passed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Kharakua%20police%20station%20is%20only%20a%20minute%E2%80%99s%20distance%20from%20our%20home.%20It%20is%20normal%20to%20hear%20protests%20and%20sloganeering%20there.%20A%20few%20policemen%20came%20to%20our%20shop%20after%20maghrib%20prayer%20and%20identified%20our%20kids.%20We%20inquired%20about%20what%