oor%20Pehelwan%20Paan%20Wale%E2%80%99.%20We%20were%20the%20fourth%20generation%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Haider%20said%2C%20infuriated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmesh%20Sharma%2C%20the%20advocate%20representing%20the%20accused%20said%20that%20the%20adult%20accused%20has%20been%20remanded%20to%20judicial%20custody%20in%20the%20central%20jail%2C%20while%20the%20other%20two%20individuals%20are%20under%20the%20custody%20of%20a%20juvenile%20home.%20He%20stated%20that%20the%20construction%20in%20question%20was%20not%20illegal.%20Even%20if%20it%20was%20deemed%20illegal%2C%20there%20should%20have%20been%20a%2024-hour%20notice%20before%20any%20action%20was%20taken.%20However%2C%20the%20authorities%20acted%20in%20a%20biased%20manner%20by%20not%20granting%20the%20family%20sufficient%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharma%20argued%20that%20punishing%20an%20entire%20family%20for%20the%20alleged%20mistakes%20of%20children%20is%20unjust%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20accused%20were%20juveniles.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20beaten%20in%20illegal%20custody%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarked%20Sharma.%20He%20further%20pointed%20out%20inconsistencies%20in%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20claims%2C%20stating%20that%20they%20referred%20to%20the%20construction%20as%20both%20illegal%20and%20dilapidated.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20did%20the%20police%20inspect%20before%20the%20Mahakal%20Sawari%3F%20%3Cem%3EPrima%20facie%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20police%20were%20under%20political%20pressure.%20The%20demolition%20is%20another%20targeted%20attack%20on%20Muslims%20before%20the%20state%20assembly%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharma%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20the%20Ujjain%20municipal%20corporation%20commissioner%20Roshan%20Kumar%20Singh.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20administration%20demolished%20the%20house%20due%20to%20its%20dilapidated%20condition.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20notice%20cited%20the%20house%20as%20dilapidated.%20We%20oversaw%20everything%20and%20followed%20all%20the%20due%20processes%20before%20demolition.%20The%20shop%20in%20question%20was%20built%20on%20a%20sewer.%20We%20conduct%20such%20drives%20on%20all%20illegal%20constructions%2C%E2%80%9D%20told%20Singh.%20However%2C%20ASP%20Akash%20Bhuria%20in%20a%20media%20address%20had%20said%20it%20was%20an%20%E2%80%9Canti-encroachment%20drive%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20a%20recent%20religious%20program%20in%20Ujjain%2C%20some%20individuals%20attempted%20to%20disturb%20religious%20harmony.%20The%20police%20registered%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20accused%20under%20various%20sections%2C%20leading%20to%20their%20subsequent%20arrest.%20We%20then%20informed%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20and%20the%20Revenue%20Department%20about%20the%20accused.%20Today%2C%20the%20illegal%20encroachment%20by%20the%20accused%20has%20been%20effectively%20removed%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20and%20the%20Revenue%20Department%2C%20and%20the%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmuslim-man-house-demolished-ujjain-amid-dj-dhol-spitting-controversy%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Quint%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20ASP%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiased%20move%2C%20says%20religious%20leader%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheher%20Qazi%20Khaliq%20Ur%20Rehman%20condemned%20the%20incident%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbiased%E2%80%9D%20move.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20administration%20took%20a%20bold%20move%20without%20verifying%20anything%20which%20not%20only%20led%20to%20the%20defamation%20of%20a%20particular%20community%20but%20also%20the%20sacred%20city%20of%20Hindus%20as%20the%20news%20went%20overseas.%20There%20must%20be%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20this%20unlawful%20demolition%20and%20the%20administration%20must%20rebuild%20the%20demolished%20home.%20Is%20it%20legal%20to%20impose%20such%20grave%20charges%20upon%20minors%3F%20If%20this%20action%20was%20not%20biased%20then%20why%20is%20an%20investigation%20pending%20in%20the%20hate%20speech%20case%20delivered%20recently%20in%20Ujjain%3F%20We%20have%20submitted%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20superintendent%20of%20police%20along%20with%20the%20proof.%20What%20is%20this%20hypocrisy%3F%E2%80%9D%20questioned%20Rehman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20editor-in-chief%20of%20Sudarshan%20News%20organising%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcjp.org.in%2Fsuresh-chavhanke-others-stoke-tensions-at-an-event-in-mp-seemingly-filled-with-hate-speech-fake-news%2F%5C%22%3Eprogramme%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20%E2%80%9CJan%20Samvad%E2%80%9D%20on%20July%207%20in%20Ujjain%2C%20where%20hate%20speeches%20were%20delivered%20against%20Muslims%20and%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20added%20that%20a%20few%20%E2%80%9Cdisruptive%20elements%E2%80%9D%20are%20attempting%20to%20harm%20the%20communal%20harmony%20of%20Ujjain%20to%20tarnish%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20peaceful%20atmosphere.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20incident%20also%20involved%20an%20outsider%2C%20who%20filmed%20a%20video%20alleging%20that%20children%20were%20spitting%20with%20malicious%20intent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20During%20the%20last%20Muharram%20procession%2C%20there%20was%20a%20baseless%20accusation%20against%20Muslims%2C%20claiming%20they%20chanted%20%E2%80%9CPakistan%20Zindabad%2C%E2%80%9D%20when%20in%20reality%2C%20they%20were%20chanting%20%E2%80%9CQazi%20Sahab%20Zindabad%E2%80%9D%2C%20Rehman%20said.%20These%20false%20allegations%20even%20led%20to%20terrorism%20charges%20against%20people%2C%20which%20were%20later%20dropped%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20attempted%20to%20contact%20SP%20Sachin%20Sharma%20and%20ASP%20Akash%20Bhuriya%20by%20phone.%20Both%20officials%20said%20they%20were%20busy%20due%20to%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Ujjain.%20However%2C%20despite%20several%20attempts%2C%20none%20of%20them%20picked%20up%20calls%20even%20later.%20Other%20officials