s%20are%20organised%20at%20Shashi%E2%80%99s%20home.%20She%20tells%20you%20her%20life%20story%20also%20which%20helps%20us%20engage%20with%20her.%20Both%2C%20Shashi%20and%20her%20son%2C%20who%20helps%20her%20in%20cooking%2C%20are%20very%20didactic%3B%20not%20only%20in%20following%20recipes%2C%20but%20also%20in%20teaching%20the%20basics%20of%20Indian%20cuisine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20love%20cooking%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20excited%20to%20use%20everything%20I%20learned%20from%20Shashi%E2%80%99s%20class%20in%20Spain.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20definitely%20put%20those%20skills%20into%20practice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20a%20five-hour%20class%2C%20the%20guests%20relish%20the%20cooked%20meals.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324597%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20a%20five-hour%20class%2C%20the%20guests%20relish%20the%20cooked%20meals.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20focus%20is%20not%20to%20only%20earn%20an%20income%20from%20these%20guests%20but%20also%20to%20treat%20them%20nicely%20because%20they%20are%20our%20guests.%20They%20should%20be%20happy%20when%20they%20go%20back%20to%20their%20homes.%20Sometimes%2C%20they%20even%20pay%20me%20extra%20on%20their%20own%20out%20of%20love.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20delectable%20meals%2C%20these%20tourists%20also%20enjoy%20Shashi%E2%80%99s%20company%2C%20who%20does%20not%20miss%20a%20chance%20to%20entertain%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20apply%20henna%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20their%20palms%20and%20help%20our%20women%20guests%20wear%20a%20saree%20with%20bangles%20and%20bindi.%20I%20also%20apply%20%3Cem%3Esindoor%20%3C%2Fem%3E(vermillion)%20to%20them.%20They%20are%20enthusiastic%20to%20participate%20in%20all%20these%20activities%20and%20show%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20knowing%20the%20Indian%20culture.%20They%20often%20request%20me%20to%20narrate%20stories%20of%20gods%20and%20goddesses%2C%20explain%20the%20significance%20of%20%3Cem%3Etulsi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(basil)%20plant%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20celebrate%20their%20birthdays.%20In%20their%20own%20dialects%2C%20they%20lovingly%20call%20me%20%E2%80%98aunty%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Shashi%2C%20teaching%20these%20foreign%20tourists%20helps%20her%20feel%20empowered.%20%E2%80%9CI%20always%20believed%20in%20hard%20work.%20No%20one%20can%20defeat%20you%20if%20you%20believe%20in%20yourself.%20%3Cem%3ERoya%20daan%20nai%20milta%2C%20aur%20maangi%20bheek%20%3C%2Fem%3E(You%20won%E2%80%99t%20always%20get%20alms%20by%20crying).%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EI%20have%20learnt%20that%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20crying%20in%20front%20of%20others%2C%20empower%20yourself%20to%20go%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689946319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebett