com%2F315247%2Fthis-single-mother-swept-streets-by-day-studied-by-night-to-become-deputy-collector%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMPSC%20result%20merit%20list%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Right%20on%20top%20was%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Khachakad%20Sunil%20Bhagwan%E2%80%99.%20The%2028-year-old%20had%20topped%20the%20exam.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Sunil%20says%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cspeechless%E2%80%9D%C2%A0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20no%20words%20to%20describe%20that%20moment.%20All%20of%20us%20were%20hugging%20each%20other%20and%20crying.%20I%20never%20imagined%20that%20I%20would%20get%20the%20first%20rank%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20result%20was%20a%20testament%20to%20seven%20years%20of%20hard%20work%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20by%20Sunil%20but%20by%20his%20family%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20journey%20of%20determination%20and%20sacrifice%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sunil%20being%20felicitated%20by%20a%20police%20officer%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250-150x200.jp