%20help%20his%20nation%20and%20began%20looking%20for%20opportunities.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20was%20around%20the%20same%20time%20that%20Sir%20Ronald%20Ross%20%E2%80%94%20a%20British%20medical%20doctor%20who%20later%20received%20the%20Nobel%20Prize%20in%201902%20for%20his%20work%20on%20the%20transmission%20of%20malaria%20%E2%80%94%20was%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20years%20of%20medical%20studies%20in%20London%2C%20Ross%20joined%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Service%20in%201881%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20his%20father%2C%20a%20General%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20It%20was%20in%201892%20during%20his%20various%20engagements%20with%20doctors%20and%20people%20from%20the%20medical%20community%20that%20Ross%20displayed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263520%2Fviral-malaria-vaccine-mosquirix-africa-india-children-who-rules%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20interest%20in%20malaria%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%20its%20mode%20of%20transmission%20from%20parasites%20to%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20526px)%20100vw%2C%20526px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F136377747_2849442258642408_8172112795104330360_n-1689681784.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22526%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20excerpt%20from%20a%20journal%20that%20highlighted%20the%20work%20of%20Kishori%20Mohan%20Bandyopadhyay%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F136377747_2849442258642408_8172112795104330360_n-1689681784.jpg%20526w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F136377747_2849442258642408_8172112795104330360_n-1689681784-232x300.jpg%20232w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F136377747_2849442258642408_8172112795104330360_n-1689681784-500x647.jpg%20500