eturned%20to%20their%20natural%20habitat%20in%20healthy%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20about%20just%20work%20for%20me%20but%20also%20the%20love%20and%20passion%20I%20have%20for%20these%20animals.%20Humans%20have%20encroached%20on%20their%20lives%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around.%20While%20the%20job%20comes%20with%20a%20set%20of%20risks%2C%20my%20main%20agenda%20is%20always%20to%20get%20the%20animal%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAlways%20an%20animal%20lover%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Meghana%20felt%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306700%2Fgrass-man-of-india-creates-grasslands-habiats-for-tigers-cheetahs-across-india-dr-gajanan-muratkar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffinity%20for%20the%20wild%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20a%20very%20young%20age.%20She%20always%20loved%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20a%20police%20officer%2C%20and%20we%20moved%20around%20a%20lot%20because%20of%20his%20transferable%20job.%20This%20led%20me%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20wildlife%20around%20the%20places%20I%20have%20lived.%20Later%20on%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%20to%20do%20my%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20Wildlife%20Sciences%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%20in%20an%20animal-loving%20family%2C%20I%20was%20constantly%20surrounded%20by%20animals.%20This%20upbringing%20made%20me%20realise%20that%20my%20future%20would%20be%20closely%20connected%20to%20the%20world%20of%20animals.%20Although%20I%20did%20not%20know%20that%20I%20would%20be%20led%20on%20to%20this%20very%20path%20I%E2%80%99m%20on%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20is%20currently%20a%20pet%20parent%20to%20two%20dogs%20and%20a%20few%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure